nodes.text: Tanjay IV was an important planet which was represented in the Galactic Senate by Nemrileo irm-Drocubac.

In The Approaching Storm, page 71, this planet is referred to as Tanjay VI. However in Tanjay IV Representative Dead in Crash-HoloNet News Vol. 531 51 it is called Tanjay IV and in The Essential Atlas it is simply named Tanjay.
